1) TO downlaod RT3070 wifi driver
	https://github.com/merces/rt3070-linux3.git
2) To recompile 
   cd $LICHEE
   ./build.sh -p sun5i -k 3.0

3) To adding some apps in buildroot
  cd $LICHEE/buildroot
  make menuconfig
 
4) To pack and download image
	cd $LICHEE/tools/pack
	./pack -csun5i -ba13-evb -plinux
